      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor road wear one would expect from a carefully driven car. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the leather seats have been regularly conditioned and show minimal creasing, while the dashboard and controls remain crisp and fully functional. Mechanically, it has been serviced religiously at scheduled intervals, resulting in a smooth, responsive drive that feels solid on the highway and agile in the city. It is a non-smoker vehicle with a fresh interior and a clear history of ownership. If you are looking for a dependable, high-quality ride that has been treated with respect, this is it.",
      "price": 34500.0,
